%20were%20conceived%20through%20IVF%2C%20so%20that%20definitely%20played%20a%20role.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f96b3265-613e-428c-aaa6-6c6b3bc10d06%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGenetic%20risks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20kids%20later%20in%20life%20does%20increase%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-kids-have-same-genetic-condition-different-outcomes-due-to-testing-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erisk%20of%20genetic%20conditions.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Bronkhurst%20emphasized%20the%20importance%20of%20Spain's%20public%20healthcare%20system%2C%20which%20was%20particularly%20beneficial%20after%20her%20second%20child%20was%20born%20with%20a%20genetic%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20getting%20pregnant%20at%20an%20older%20age%20can%20increase%20the%20likelihood%20of%20complications%2C%20Bronkhurst%20said%20that%20in%20countries%20with%20universal%20healthcare%20and%20a%20high%20standard%20of%20medical%20care%2C%20the%20perceived%20risk%20of%20advanced-age%20pregnancy%20is%20significantly%20lower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20plays%20into%20the%20whole%20thing%20of%20waiting%20longer%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2298db9a40-6448-44cc-8077-5938aa7f1df7%5C%22%3ESlow%20to%20settle%20down%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20major%20factor%20contributing%20to%20delayed%20motherhood%20in%20Spain%20is%20that%20people%20are%20simply%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-married-older-focus-career-finances-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esettling%20down%20later%20in%20life.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20age%20of%20first%20marriage%20among%20men%20in%20Spain%20is%2036.8%2C%20the%20highest%20in%20Europe%2C%20while%20for%20women%20it's%2034.7%2C%20also%20the%20highest%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fec.europa.eu%2Feurostat%2Fdatabrowser%2Fview%2Ftps00014%2Fdefault%2Ftabl