Fjd-vances-christmas-biscuit-baking-tradition-with-daughter-wows-social-media-what-a-great-little-assistant%2Farticleshow%2F116649900.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjd-vances-christmas-biscuit-baking-tradition-with-daughter-wows-social-media-what-a-great-little-assistant%2Famp_articleshow%2F116649900.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjd-vances-christmas-biscuit-baking-tradition-with-daughter-wows-social-media-what-a-great-little-assistant%2Famp_articleshow%2F116649900.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20doctor%20who%20says%20he's%20reversed%20his%20age%20by%2020%20years%20shares%20the%206%20bare-minimum%20things%20you%20can%20do%20to%20live%20longer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20Dr.%20Michael%20Roizen's%20headshot%2C%20someone%20playing%20a%20game%20on%20their%20phone%2C%20and%20some%20pills%20spilling%20out%20of%20a%20bottle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d6dd4814a5cd1fcc8c8ad9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDr.%20Michael%20Roizen%20shared%20some%20bare-minimum%20things%20you%20can%20do%20to%20live%20longer%2C%20including%20playing%20games%20for%20brain%20health%20and%20taking%20a%20multivitamin.%3Cp%3EDr.%20Michael%20Roizen%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDr.%20Michael%20Roizen%20is%20a%20longevity%20expert%20who%20says%20he's%20reversed%20his%20age%20by%2020%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere%20are%20a%20few%20bare-minimum%20things%20you%20can%20do%20to%20live%20longer%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThese%20include%20getting%20vaccinated%2C%20playing%20brain-training%20games%2C%20and%20eating%20salmon.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20be%20tough%20to%20find%20the%20time%20to%20take%20care%20of%20our%20health.%20But%20a%20doctor%20who%20says%20he's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupplements-doctor-reverse-age-years-takes-roizen-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereversed%20his%20age%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%2020%20years%20believes%20focusing%20on%20six%20basics%20could%20help%20us%20stay%20healthy%20for%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Michael%20Roizen%2C%2078%2C%20the%20chief%20wellness%20officer%20at%20Cleveland%20Clinic%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20his%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiological-age-test-calculation-interpret-results-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebiological%20age%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20was%2057.6%2C%20based%20on%20the%20health%20of%20his%20organs%20and%20his%20risk%20of%20chronic%20disease.%20(There's%20no%20agreed%20definition%20of%20biological%20age%20or%20how%20it%20can%20be%20measured.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoizen%20is%20all%20about%20finding%20lifestyle%20changes%20that%20can%20help%20people%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoctor-longevity-expert-reverse-biological-age-years-diet-principle-s2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elive%20healthily%20for%20as%20long%20as%20possible%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20he%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20are%20small%20things%20and%20easy%20things%20to%20do%20that%20make%20a%20big%20difference%26quot%3B%20to%20longevity%2C%20even%20if%20people%20can't%20overhaul%20their%20lifestyles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelow%20are%20the%20six%20things%20he%20thinks%20everyone%20should%20do%20to%20live%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e15e44e7-2fdb-4696-a9ce-cdc253922e3e%5C%22%3EWalk%20more%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERoizen%20tries%20to%20do%2010%2C000%20steps%20a%20day%20as%20part%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusy-doctor-reversed-age-20-years-workout-routine-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehis%20weekly%20workout%20routine%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20said%20everyone%20should%20%26quot%3Btry%20to%20walk%20a%20little%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20add%20movement%20to%20his%20commute%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20he%20parks%20his%20car%20as%20far%20away%20from%20his%20work%20as%20possible%20and%20walks%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalking%20fewer%20than%2010%2C000%20steps%20%E2%80%94%20a%20somewhat%20arbitrary%20number%20with%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalking-10000-steps-for-health-not-science-based-in-marketing-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorigins%20in%20marketing%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20still%20has%20benefits.%20One%202023%20study%20by%20researchers%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Cambridge%20in%20the%20UK%20found%20that%20people%20who%20briskly%20walked%20for%2075%20minutes%20a%20week%20had%20a%20lower%20risk%20of%20dying%20from%20any%20cause%20or%20developing%20cardiovascular%20diseases%20and%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2238db1c68-d343-4773-a8fa-922c8698a10b%5C%22%3EEat%20avocado%2C%20salmon%2C%20and%20olive%20oil%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20previously%20reported%20on%20the%20seven%20foods%20Roizen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoctor-reverse-age-years-foods-eat-weekly-longevity-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeats%20for%20longevity%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20he%20said%20that%20eating%20just%20three%20of%20these%20%E2%80%94%20avocado%2C%20salmon%2C%20and%20olive%20oil%20%E2%80%94%20would%20still%20merit%20health%20benefits.%20Studies%20have%20linked%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eall%20three%20to%20a%20lower%20risk%20of%20cardiovascular%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228d4db1b7-e624-4850-829c-34e784eeffef%5C%22%3EHave%20strong%20relationships%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENurturing%20friendships%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bfun%26quot%3B%20way%20to%20boost%20health%20and%20longevity%2C%20Roizen%20said.%20Plus%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20always%20better%20to%20do%20things%20with%20other%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERose%20Anne%20Kenny%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20aging%20who's%20the%20lead%20researcher%20on%20The%20Irish%20Longitudinal%20Study%20on%20Ageing%20at%20Trinity%20College%20Dublin%2C%20said%20having%20strong%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-antiaging-friendship-social-interaction-relationships-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20connections%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20just%20as%20important%20for%20longevity%20as%20a%20healthy%20diet%20and%20getting%20enough%20exercise%2C%20BI%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2285404f61-1679-43fb-9ce4-3f098f48af03%5C%22%3EPlay%20speed-of-processing%20games%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222120%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20playing%20a%20game%20on%20their%20phone.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d6de271d8d2deb96b81063%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPlaying%20speed-of-processing%20games%20could%20benefit%20brain%20health%2C%20Roizen%20said.%3Cp%3EWitthaya%20Prasongsin%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERoizen%20recommended%20playing%20speed-of-processing%20games%2C%20which%20are%20brain-training%20games%20that%20research%20suggests%20may%20help%20improve%20how%20quickly%20your%20brain%20works.%20Roizen%20recommended%20two%3A%20%26quot%3BDouble%20Decision%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BFreeze%20Frame.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReferencing%20a%202017%20study%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS2352873717300598%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlzheimer's%20%26amp%3B%20Dementia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Roizen%20said%20practicing%20these%20games%20could%20reduce%20the%20risk%20of%20dementia.%20The%20study%20found%20that%20older%20adults%20who%20played%2010%20sessions%20of%20these%20games%20over%20an%20initial%20six-week%20period%20and%20then%20did%20top-up%20sessions%2011%20and%2035%20months%20later%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehad%20a%2029%25%20lower%20risk%20of%20dementia%20after%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoizen%20recommended%20playing%20these%20games%20for%20two%20hours%20a%20week%20for%20five%20weeks%20to%20try%20to%20replicate%20the%20study%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ea3bd378-f4c6-42f1-adc9-e27c622feaab%5C%22%3ETake%20a%20multivitamin%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EResearch%20is%20mixed%20on%20whether%20taking%20multivitamins%20is%20beneficial%20for%20longevity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoizen%20cited%20studies%20that%20found%20the%20risks%20of%20cancer%2C%20cardiovascular%20disease%2C%20and%20dementia%20were%20reduced%20in%20people%20who%20took%20multivitamins%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20recent%20research%20has%20suggested%20these%20findings%20don't%20necessarily%20indicate%20that%20multivitamins%20are%20as%20effective%20outside%20study%20conditions.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20large%20study%20on%20more%20than%20390%2C000%20people%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjamanetworkopen%2Ffullarticle%2F2820369%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJAMA%20Network%20Open%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20year%20concluded%20that%20taking%20a%20multivitamin%20wasn't%20linked%20to%20longevity.%20And%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjama%2Ffullarticle%2F2793446%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20Preventive%20Services%20Task%20Force%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20recommend%20the%20general%20public%20take%20multivitamins%20because%20there's%20not%20enough%20evidence%20to%20show%20it%20has%20any%20benefit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoizen%20said%20he%20takes%20a%20multivitamin%20anyway%20to%20keep%20the%20overall%20levels%20of%20vitamins%20in%20his%20body%20stable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225f6f6720-7198-428e-9df9-a7fc9c99e882%5C%22%3EGet%20your%20flu%20shot%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Centers%20for%20Disease%20Control%20and%20Prevention%20recommends%20that%20everyone%20age%20six%20months%20and%20above%20should%20get%20a%20flu%20vaccine%20every%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Roizen%20also%20takes%20it%20for%20the%20potential%20healthy-aging%20benefits.%20A%202022%20review%20of%20studies%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS1568163721002816%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAgeing%20Research%20Reviews%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggested%20that%20vaccinating%20older%20people%20against%20the%20flu%20could%20also%20help%20prevent%20dementia%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Epossibly%20because%20it%20decreases%20inflammation%20in%20the%20brain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-expert-doctor-bare-minimum-tips-to-live-longer-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735113901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d6dd4814a5cd1fcc8c8ad9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-expert-doctor-bare-minimum-tips-to-live-longer-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20doctor%20who%20says%20he's%20as%20healthy%20as%20someone%2020%20years%20his%20junior%20believes%20walking%20is%20a%20key%20part%20of%20his%20daily%20routine.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22skenny%40businessinsider.com%20(Serafina%20Kenny)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-expert-doctor-bare-minimum-tips-to-live-longer-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hydroponic%20ganja%20from%20Thailand%20new%20headache%20for%20Chennai%20airport%20security%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735113656000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116651338%2Cimgsize-972349.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fchennai%2Fhydroponic-ganja-fr