20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUniversal%20basic%20income%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20UBI%2C%20typically%20refers%20to%20making%20recurring%20cash%20payments%20to%20all%20adults%20in%20a%20population%2C%20regardless%20of%20their%20wealth%20or%20employment%20status%2C%20and%20with%20no%20restrictions%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-people-spend-universal-basic-income-ubi-food-housing-transportation-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehow%20they%20spend%20the%20money%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERhodes%20headed%20up%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20studies%20in%20the%20space%2C%20which%20focused%20specifically%20on%20those%20on%20low%20incomes%20rather%20than%20making%20universal%20payments%20to%20adults%20across%20all%20economic%20demographics.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20three-year%20experiment%2C%20backed%20by%20OpenAI%20boss%20Altman%2C%20provided%201%2C000%20low-income%20participants%20with%20%241%2C000%20a%20month%20without%20any%20stipulations%20for%20how%20they%20could%20spend%20it.%20The%20study%20aimed%20to%20explore%20how%20unconditional%20cash%20payments%20influence%20various%20aspects%20of%20recipients'%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20findings%2C%20released%20in%20July%2C%20found%20that%20recipients%20put%20the%20bulk%20of%20their%20extra%20spending%20toward%20basic%20needs%20such%20as%20rent%2C%20transportation%2C%20and%20food.%20They%20also%20worked%20less%20on%20average%20but%20remained%20engaged%20in%20the%20workforce%20and%20were%20more%20deliberate%20in%20their%20job%20searches%20compared%20with%20a%20control%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Rhodes%20says%20the%20research%20reinforced%20how%20difficult%20it%20is%20to%20solve%20complex%20issues%20such%20as%20poverty%20or%20economic%20insecurity%2C%20and%20that%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20more%20work%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Altman-backed%20study%20is%20still%20reporting%20results.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-basic-income-study-new-findings-work-ubi-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20findings%20released%20in%20December%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed%20recipients%20valued%20work%20more%20after%20receiving%20the%20recurring%20monthly%20payments%20%E2%80%94%20a%20result%20that%20may%20challenge%20one%20of%20the%20main%20arguments%20against%20basic%20income%20payments.%20Participants%20also%20reported%20significant%20reductions%20in%20stress%2C%20mental%20distress%2C%20and%20food%20insecurity%20during%20the%20first%20year%2C%20though%20those%20effects%20faded%20by%20the%20second%20and%20third%20years%20of%20the%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPoverty%20and%20economic%20insecurity%20are%20incredibly%20difficult%20problems%20to%20solve%2C%26quot%3B%20Rhodes%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20findings%20that%20we've%20had%20thus%20far%20are%20quite%20nuanced.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThere's%20not%20a%20clear%20through%20line%20in%20terms%20of%2C%20this%20helps%20everyone%2C%20or%20this%20does%20that.%20It%20reinforced%20to%20me%20the%20idea%20that%20these%20are%20really%20difficult%20problems%20that%2C%20maybe%2C%20there%20isn't%20a%20singular%20solution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a6324289-f487-44f9-9f37-d0cb54a3f8d5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUBI%20and%20Silcion%20Valley%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUniversal%20basic%20income%20has%20garnered%20significant%20support%20within%20Silicon%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20programs%20have%20long%20been%20a%20passion%20project%20for%20high-profile%20tech%20leaders%2C%20including%20Twitter%20cofounder%20Jack%20Dorsey%2C%20Meta%20CEO%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Tesla%20chief%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20t