ising%2C%20Rhodes%20said%2C%20as%20the%20team%20never%20saw%20the%20experiment%20as%20a%20policy%20suggestion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20never%20designed%20to%20be%20a%20policy%20referendum%20on%20UBI%20or%20any%20specific%20policy.%20It%20was%20an%20opportunity%20to%20really%20ask%20the%20sort%20of%20big%2C%20open-ended%20questions%2C%20you%20know%2C%20what%20happens%20when%20you%20give%20people%20unconditional%20cash%20to%20better%20understand%20the%20lived%20experiences%20of%20lower-income%20Americans%20and%20the%20challenges%20they%20were%20facing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fubi-sam-altman-study-universal-basic-income-researcher-gbi-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735113602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6758883c91c1cc343d47b254%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fubi-sam-altman-study-universal-basic-income-researcher-gbi-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elizabeth%20Rhodes%20says%20the%20study's%20results%20so%20far%20suggest%20there%20%26quot%3Bisn't%20a%20singular%20solution%26quot%3B%20for%20addressing%20poverty%20and%20economic%20insecurity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bnolan%40insider.com%20(Beatrice%20Nolan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fubi-sam-altman-study-universal-basic-income-researcher-gbi-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anushka-Virat's%20Melbourne%20Xmas%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735113555000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116651191%2Cimgsize-71354.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fanushka-sharma-and-virat-kohli-celebrate-christmas-2024-in-melbourne-cozy-breakfas