aijan-airlines-passenger-plane-crashes-in-kazakhstan-bursts-into-flames%2Famp_articleshow%2F116650451.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fwatch-azerbaijan-airlines-passenger-plane-crashes-in-kazakhstan-bursts-into-flames%2Famp_articleshow%2F116650451.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Atishi%20Will%20Be%20Arrested%20In%20Fake%20Case%20Ahead%20Of%20Delhi%20Polls%3A%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECentral%20agencies%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20arrest%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Atishi%20and%20raid%20the%20homes%20of%20all%20senior%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leaders%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20disrupt%20AAP's%20Assembly%20polls%20preparations%2C%20the%20party's%20national%20convener%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20meet%20hours%20after%20two%20Delhi%20departments%20red-flagged%20the%20Atishi-led%20government's%20Mahila%20Samman%20Yojana%20and%20Sanjeevani%20Yojana%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%20the%20BJP%20has%20conspired%20to%20inconvenience%20Delhi%20residents%20for%20the%20past%2010%20years.%20%26quot%3BThey%20kept%20stopping%20Delhi%20government's%20work%20through%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor.%20But%20the%20Delhi%20government%20kept%20working.%20When%20all%20these%20conspiracies%20failed%2C%20they%20started%20sending%20top%20AAP%20leaders%20and%20ministers%20to%20jail.%20Work%20still%20did%20not%20stop.%20The%20BJP%20can%20now%20see%20it%20is%20headed%20for%20a%20historic%20defeat.%20They%20have%20no%20narrative%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20national%20convener%20said%20BJP%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bhalf-government%26quot%3B%20in%20Delhi%20with%20seven%20MPs%20and%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor.%20%26quot%3BIn%20these%2010%20years%2C%20they%20did%20not%20build%20a%20single%20road%2C%20hospital%2C%20school%2C%20or%20college.%20Delhi's%20people%20gave%20them%20one%20job%3A%20law%20and%20order.%20They%20ruined%20that%20too.%20People%20are%20living%20in%20fear.%20They%20can't%20say%20what%20work%20they%20have%20done%20and%20what%20they%20will%20do%20if%20you%20vote%20for%20them.%20They%20are%20just%20abusing%20Kejriwal%20and%20asking%20for%20votes.%20They%20have%20no%20Chief%20Minister%20face%20or%20agenda%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20running%20a%20positive%20campaign.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20telling%20people%20about%20our%20work%2C%20we%20bettered%20schools%2C%20and%20hospitals%2C%20provided%20free%20power%20round%20the%20clock%2C%20gave%20water%20supply%2C%20brought%20free%20bus%20rides%20for%20women%2C%20pilgrimages%20for%20elderly.%20And%20then%20we%20are%20asking%20for%20votes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20said%20there%20is%20immense%20excitement%20among%20Delhi%20residents%20to%20register%20for%20Mahila%20Samman%20Yojana%20promising%20Rs%202%2C100%20for%20women%20every%20month%20and%20Sanjeevani%20Yojana%20for%20free%20treatment%20to%20the%20elderly.%20%26quot%3BThis%20has%20rattled%20the%20BJP%2C%20we%20have%20come%20to%20know%20from%20our%20sources%20that%20ED%2C%20CBI%20and%20Income%20Tax%20have%20met.%20There%20are%20orders%20from%20the%20top%20to%20arrest%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Atishi%20in%20a%20false%20case.%20Before%20that%2C%20senior%20AAP%20leaders%2C%20including%20me%2C%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%2C%20Satyendra%20Jain.%20The%20objective%20is%20to%20distract%20us%20from%20the%20poll%20campaign%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20leader%20alleged%20that%20a%20false%20case%20is%20being%20prepped%20against%20Atishi%20in%20the%20Delhi%20transport%20department%20and%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20stop%20free%20bus%20rides%20for%20women.%20%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20people%20will%20reply%20to%20this%20dirty%20conspiracy.%20The%20people%20of%20this%20country%20do%20not%20support%20this%20kind%20of%20politics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BNotices%20Are%20Lies%26quot%3B%3A%20Atishi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Atishi%20said%20that%20truth%20shall%20prevail%20even%20if%20she%20is%20arrested%20in%20a%20false%20case.%20%26quot%3BWe%20trust%20the%20judiciary.%20They%20sent%20all%20our%20top%20leaders%20to%20jail%20in%20false%20cases%2C%20but%20the%20truth%20eventually%20came%20out%20and%20they%20got%20bail.%26quot%3B%20She%20said%20the%20BJP%20must%20know%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bpeople%20are%20watching%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20newspaper%20notices%20issued%20by%20Delhi's%20health%20and%20women%20and%20child%20development%20departments%2C%20blocking%20the%20two%20schemes%20announced%20by%20AAP%2C%20Ms%20Atishi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20notices%20published%20in%20newspapers%20are%20wrong%2C%20lies.%20BJP%20has%20pressured%20officials%20and%20got%20this%20wrong%20information%20published%20in%20newspapers.%20These%20officials%20will%20face%20administrative%20as%20well%20as%20police%20action.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20notice%20that%20said%20there%20was%20no%20Mahila%20Samman%20Yojana%2C%20she%20held%20up%20a%20piece%20of%20paper%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDelhi%20government%20has%20taken%20a%20cabinet%20decision%20on%20the%20Mahila%20Samman%20Yojana%20and%20this%20notification%20is%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20We%20have%20notified%20the%20scheme%20to%20provide%20Rs%201%2C000%20per%20month%20to%20women.%20Later%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20gave%20a%20guarantee%20that%20we%20would%20provide%20Rs%202%2C100%20per%20month%20when%20we%20form%20the%20government%20after%20the%20election.%20He%20also%20announced%20Sanjeevani%20Yojana%20to%20provide%20free%20medical%20treatment%20to%20the%20elderly.%20This%20is%20clearly%20AAP's%20announcement%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20guarantee%20that%20Sanjeevani%20will%20be%20brought%20and%20amount%20hiked%20to%20Rs%202%2C100%20after%20the%20government%20is%20formed.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735111500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fq1pilngo_kejriwal-atishi_625x300_25_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fatishi-will-be-arrested-in-fake-case-ahead-of-delhi-polls-alleges-arvind-kejriwal-7327667%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Central%20agencies%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20arrest%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Atishi%20in%20a%20fake%20case%20and%20raid%20the%20homes%20of%20all%20senior%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leaders%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20disrupt%20the%20party's%20Assembly%20polls%20preparations%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20said%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fatishi-will-be-arrested-in-fake-case-ahead-of-delhi-polls-alleges-arvind-kejriwal-7327667%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BRattled%26quot%3B%3A%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20After%20Delhi%20Departments%20Red-Flag%20Key%20AAP%20Schemes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20dramatic%20developments%20amid%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party's%20(AAP)%20campaign%20for%20Delhi%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20capital's%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%20department%20has%20red-flagged%20the%20ruling%20AAP's%20registration%20drive%20for%20Sanjeevani%20Yojana%2C%20a%20scheme%20to%20provide%20free%20treatment%20to%20Delhi's%20residents%20aged%20over%2060%20at%20private%20and%20government%20hospitals.%20Also%2C%20the%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20department%20has%20disowned%20the%20Mahila%20Samman%20Yojana%20which%20promises%20Rs%202%2C100%20per%20month%20to%20women%20in%20the%20capital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20public%20notice%20published%20in%20newspapers%2C%20the%20health%20department%20has%20said%20that%20it%20does%20not%20have%20%26quot%3Bany%20such%20supposed%20Sanjeevani%20scheme%20in%20existence%26quot%3B.%20It%20added%20that%20it%20had%20not%20authorised%20anyone%20to%20collect%20personal%20data%20from%20elderly%20citizens%20and%20is%20not%20providing%20any%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20after%20AAP%20leaders%2C%20including%20Chief%20Minister%20Atishi%20and%20party%20convener%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20visited%20several%20areas%20and%20launched%20doorstep%20registration%20for%20Sanjeevani%20Yojana%20and%20Mahila%20Samman%20Yojana.%20The%20AAP%20has%20also%20come%20out%20with%20an%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20ad%20with%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20in%20a%20Santa%20Claus%20avatar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EDelhi's%20own%20Santa%20delivering%20gifts%20year-round%20%E2%9C%A8%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FMerryChristmas%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23MerryChristmas%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fkm2IOdAPoQ%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fkm2IOdAPoQ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20AAP%20(%40AamAadmiParty)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAamAadmiParty%2Fstatus%2F1871779894444834819%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2025%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20said%20any%20individual%20or%20political%20party%20collecting%20such%20forms%20under%20the%20name%20of%20this%20scheme%20is%20%26quot%3Bfraudulent%20and%20without%20any%20authority%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20person%2Fentity%20calls%20you%20or%20visits%20you%20with%20the%20promise%20to%20provide%20benefit%20of%20free%20treatment%20under%20this%20supposed%20non-existent%20scheme%20or%20provide%20you%20some%20%26quot%3BHealth%2FSanjeevani%20Scheme%20Card%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20then%20you%20are%20hereby%20advised%20to%3A%20(1)%20not%20believe%20in%20any%20promise%20of%20free%20treatment%20under%20the%20supposed%20non-existent%20%26quot%3BSanjeevani%20scheme%26quot%3B%20(2)%20not%20to%20provide%20any%20personal%20detail%20to%20anybody%20claiming%20to%20provide%20benefits%20under%20the%20scheme%20(3)%20not%20to%20affix%20your%20signature%20or%20thumbprint%20on%20any%20document%20unknowingly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20has%20said%20it%20will%20not%20be%20responsible%20for%20any%20liabilities%20or%20frauds%20arising%20out%20of%20such%20%26quot%3Bunscrupulous%20activities%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20department%20said%20in%20a%20notice%20that%20no%20scheme%20called%20Mahila%20Samman%20Yojana%20has%20been%20notified.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%2C%20if%20and%20when%20such%20a%20scheme%20is%20notified%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20(WCD)%2C%20GNCTD%2C%20will%20launch%20a%20digital%20portal%20for%20eligible%20individuals%20to%20submit%20their%20applications%20online%20as%20per%20the%20approved%20guidelines.%20The%20eligibility%20conditions%20and%20modalities%20will%20be%20clearly%20notified%20by%20the%20department%20as%20and%20when%20it%20happens.%C2%A0It%20is%20emphasized%20that%20since%20no%20such%20scheme%20exists%2C%20the%20question%20of%20physical%20forms%20%2F%20applications%20for%20the%20registration%20under%20this%20non-existent%20scheme%20does%20not%20arise%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20any%20individual%20collecting%20forms%20or%20information%20in%20the%20name%20of%20this%20scheme%20is%C2%A0%26quot%3Bfraudulent%20and%20without%20any%20authority%26quot%3B.%C2%A0The%20department%20has%20warned%20that%20sharing%20personal%20information%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20may%20lead%20to%20people%20falling%20prey%20to%20cybercrime.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20the%20notices%20were%20issued%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20targeted%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Mahila%20Samman%20Yojana%20and%20Sanjeevani%20Yojana%20have%20rattled%20them.%20Within%20the%20next%20few%20days%2C%20they%20plan%20to%20arrest%20Atishi%20ji%20in%20a%20fake%20case.%20Before%20that%2C%20senior%20AAP%20leaders%20would%20be%20raided%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20AAP%20sources%2C%201.5%20lakh%20people%20have%20been%20registered%20for%20the%20Sanjeevani%20scheme%20so%20far%20and%2013%20lakh%20women%20for%20Mahila%20Samman%20Yojana.%20A%20team%20of%203%2C000%20AAP%20workers%20are%20carrying%20out%20the%20doorstep%20registrations%20with%20a%20target%20of%205%20lakh%20registrations%20daily%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20BJP%20chief%20Virendraa%20Sachdeva%20said%20it%20was%20deplorable%20that%20Delhi%20government%20was%20%26quot%3Bdoing%20what%20digital%20fraudsters%20do%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%26quot%3BThey%20are%20misleading%20women%20and%20the%20elderly%20by%20bringing%20schemes%20without%20notification.%20First%20time%20in%20history%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20ruling%20party%20are%20peddling%20fake%20schemes%20after%2010%20years%20in%20power.%20Dutiful%20officials%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20issue%20a%20public%20warning%20to%20spread%20public%20awareness%20and%20protect%20people%20from%20getting%20misled%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20departments'%20notices%20play%20out%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20power%20tussle%20between%20Delhi's%20elected%20government%20and%20the%20Centre.%20The%20principal%20secretaries%20of%20all%20Delhi%20departments%20report%20to%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%2C%20a%20central%20government%20appointee.%20This%2C%20in%20effect%2C%20means%20that%20the%20AAP%20government%20has%20no%20control%20over%20Delhi%20officers%2C%20an%20issue%20it%20has%20repeatedly%20raised%20in%20its%2010-year%20rule%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20last%20year%20that%20the%20Delhi%20government%20would%20control%20the%20services%20in%20the%20capital%2C%20but%20the%20Centre%20brought%20an%20ordinance%20and%20then%20an%20Act%20to%20overturn%20this.%20This%20Act%20established%20National%20Capital%20Civil%20Services%20Authority%2C%20comprising%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20Delhi%20Chief%20Secretary%20and%20Principal%20Home%20Secretary.%20This%20Authority%20makes%20recommendations%20to%20Delhi's%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20on%20officials'%20transfers%20and%20postings%20and%20disciplinary%20matters.%20The%20Chief%20Secretary%20and%20Principal%20Home%20Secretary%20are%20the%20Centre's%20appointees%20and%20can%20easily%20outvote%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735111200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Ftp6hhjfg_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_25_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-election-delhi-health-department-red-flags-sanjeevani-scheme-arvind-kejriwal-reacts-7326976%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20dramatic%20developments%20amid%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party's%20(AAP)%20campaign%20for%20Delhi%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20capital's%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%20department%20has%20red-flagged%20the%20ruling%20AAP's%20registration%20drive%20for%20Sanjeevani%20Yojana%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-election-delhi-health-department-red-flags-sanjeevani-scheme-arvind-kejriwal-reacts-7326976%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vinod%20Kambli%20assured%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%20assistance%20by%20Shiv%20Sena%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735111173000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116650456%2Cimgsize-39264.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fvinod-kambli-assured-of-all-possible-help-by-shiv-sena%2Farticleshow%2F116650461.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shiv%20Sena%20has%20pledged%20support%20for%20former%20cricketer%20Vin