ing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMartin%20was%20the%20single-biggest%20donor%20to%20political%20parties%2C%20purchasing%20over%20Rs%201%2C300%20crore%20worth%20of%20now-scrapped%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20through%20his%20firm%20Future%20Gaming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprobe-agency-seizes-rs-8-8-crore-from-lottery-king-santiago-martins-office-7026858%5C%22%3EIn%20November%2C%20the%20probe%20agency%20carried%20out%20searches%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20several%20states%20as%20part%20of%20the%20money%20laundering%20probe%20against%20the%20'lottery%20king'.%20At%20least%2020%20premises%20linked%20to%20Martin%2C%20his%20son-in-law%20Aadhav%20Arjun%20and%20associates%20in%20Chennai%20and%20Coimbatore%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Faridabad%20in%20Haryana%2C%20Ludhiana%20in%20Punjab%20and%20Kolkata%20in%20West%20Bengal%20were%20searched%20as%20part%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bcomprehensive%26quot%3B%20action%20against%20his%20business%20empire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20agency%20seized%20at%20least%20Rs%208.8%20crore%20cash%20during%20the%20searches.%20It%20came%20after%20the%20Madras%20High%20Court%20allowed%20the%20probe%20agency%20to%20proceed%20against%20Martin%20when%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Police%20had%20closed%20the%20primary%20case%20against%20him%20and%20a%20few%20others%20and%20the%20trial%20court%20had%20accepted%20the%20cops'%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20the%20CBI%20registered%20the%20case%20in%20the%20alleged%20lottery%20scam%20and%20filed%20a%20chargesheet%20against%20Martin%20and%20others.%20Based%20on%20the%20chargesheet%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20filed%20a%20complaint%20against%20seven%20people%20including%20Martin%20for%20money%20laundering%20in%20June%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202024%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-stays-trial-in-money-laundering-case-against-lottery-king-santiago-martin-5413599%5C%22%3Ethe%20Supr