with%20US%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20(NSA)%20Jake%20Sullivan%2C%20Bangladesh's%20interim%20government%20chief%20Muhammad%20Yunus%20expressed%20commitment%20to%20protect%20human%20rights%20in%20the%20troubled%20South%20Asian%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20leaders%20expressed%20their%20commitment%20to%20respecting%20and%20protecting%20the%20human%20rights%20of%20all%20people%2C%20regardless%20of%20religion%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20White%20House%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20about%20the%20call%20between%20Mr%20Sullivan%20and%20Mr%20Yunus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20call%20comes%20less%20than%20a%20month%20before%20the%20Biden%20administration%20is%20set%20to%20pass%20on%20the%20power%20to%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20would%20be%20sworn%20in%20as%20the%2047th%20President%20of%20the%20United%20States%20on%20January%2020%20next%20year.%20It%20also%20came%20at%20the%20backdrop%20of%20attacks%20on%20Bangladesh's%20Hindu%20minority%20and%20their%20places%20of%20worship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sullivan%20during%20the%20call%20thanked%20Yunus%20for%20his%20leadership%20of%20Bangladesh%20during%20a%20challenging%20period%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSullivan%20re-iterated%20the%20United%20States'%20support%20for%20a%20prosperous%2C%20stable%2C%20and%20democratic%20Bangladesh%2C%20and%20offered%20the%20United%20States'%20continued%20support%20in%20meeting%20the%20challenges%20Bangladesh%20faces%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20readout%20of%20the%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOutrage%20Of%20Killing%20of%20Hindus%20In%20Bangladesh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20a%20spate%20of%20incidents%20of%20violence%20against%20Hindus%20and%20other%20minorities%2C%20as%20well%20as%20attacks%20on%20temples%20in%20Bangladesh%20after%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20Hasina%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2013%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said%20that%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20is%20closely%20monitoring%20the%20situation%20in%20Bangladesh%20and%20the%20US%20will%20hold%20the%20country's%20interim%20government%20accountable%20for%20ensuring%20the%20protection%20of%20religious%20and%20ethnic%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conversation%20between%20Mr%20Sullivan%20and%20Mr%20Yunus%20comes%20days%20after%20Indian%20American%20Democratic%20Congressman%20Shri%20Thanedar%20urged%20the%20White%20House%20to%20strongly%20raise%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20killing%20of%20Hindus%20and%20destruction%20of%20their%20temples%20in%20Bangladesh%20with%20the%20head%20of%20the%20country's%20interim%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20United%20States%20has%20a%20storied%20history%20of%20championing%20the%20oppressed%20and%20this%20issue%20should%20be%20no%20different.%20When%20we%20receive%20a%20global%20call%20for%20help%2C%20we%20must%20respond%20appropriately%20as%20the%20world's%20bellwether%20of%20human%20rights.%20We%20must%20urge%20Prime%20Minister%20Muhammad%20Yunus%20to%20fulfil%20his%20promise%20of%20restoring%20peace%20and%20rebuilding%20the%20nation%20on%20principles%20of%20equality%20and%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20Thanedar%20said%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocacy%20group%20HinduAction%20said%20that%20disturbing%20reports%20of%20brutal%20attacks%20against%20the%20Hindus%20continue%20to%20surface%2C%20particularly%20over%20the%20past%20two%20weeks%2C%20as%20desperate%20pleas%20for%20help%20pour%20in%20from%20those%20affected%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHinduACTion%20executive%20director%20Utsav%20Chakrabarti%20said%20what%20has%20happened%20in%20the%20last%20five%20and%20half%20months%20in%20Bangladesh%20clearly%20reflects%20that%20%26quot%3BMuhammad%20Yunus%20has%20failed%20to%20contain%26quot%3B%20his%20allies%20in%20the%20Jamaat-e-Islami%20who%20are%20now%20running%20around%20the%20country%2C%20burning%20temples%2C%20killing%20people%2C%20raping%20women%20and%20indulging%20in%20atrocities%20against%20priests%20and%