oot%20borewell%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Kotputli-Behror%20district.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fover-40-hours-on-girl-3-still-stuck-at-150-foot-in-borewell-in-rajasthan-7326830%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BStands%20Tall%20As%20A%20Statesman%26quot%3B%3A%20PM%20Modi%20Remembers%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAtal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20stands%20tall%20as%20a%20statesman%20and%20continues%20to%20inspire%20countless%20people%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20wrote%20today%2C%20paying%20tribute%20to%20the%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20on%20his%20birth%20centenary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20nation%20will%20always%20be%20grateful%20to%20Atal%20Ji%20for%20being%20the%20architect%20of%20India's%20transition%20into%20the%2021st%20century.%20When%20he%20took%20oath%20as%20PM%20in%201998%20our%20nation%20had%20passed%20through%20a%20period%20of%20political%20instability.%20In%20about%209%20years%2C%20we%20had%20seen%204%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20The%20people%20of%20India%20were%20getting%20impatient%20and%20also%20sceptical%20about%20governments%20being%20able%20to%20deliver.%20It%20was%20Atal%20Ji%20who%20turned%20this%20tide%20by%20providing%20stable%20and%20effective%20governance.%20Coming%20from%20humble%20roots%2C%20he%20realised%20the%20struggles%20of%20the%20common%20citizen%20and%20the%20transformative%20power%20of%20effective%20governance%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20said%20the%20Vajpayee%20era%20marked%20a%20gigantic%20leap%20for%20the%20Information%20Technology%2C%20telecom%20and%20communications%20sectors.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20particularly%20important%20for%20a%20nation%20like%20ours%2C%20which%20is%20also%20blessed%20with%20a%20very%20dynamic%20Yuva%20Shakti.%20The%20NDA%20Government%20under%20Atal%20Ji%20made%20the%20first%20serious%20attempt%20to%20make%20technology%20accessible%20to%20the%20common%20citizens.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20there%20was%20foresight%20in%20connecting%20India.%20Even%20today%2C%20most%20people%20recall%20the%20Golden%20Quadrilateral%20Project%2C%20which%20connected%20the%20length%20and%20breadth%20of%20India.%20Equally%20notable%20were%20the%20Vajpayee%20Government's%20efforts%20to%20enhance%20local%20connectivity%20as%20well%20through%20initiatives%20like%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Gram%20Sadak%20Yojana.%20Similarly%2C%20his%20Government%20gave%20a%20push%20to%20metro%20connectivity%20by%20doing%20extensive%20work%20for%20the%20Delhi%20Metro%2C%20which%20stands%20out%20as%20a%20world-class%20infrastructure%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThus%2C%20the%20Vajpayee%20Government%20not%20only%20boosted%20economic%20growth%20but%20also%20brought%20distant%20regions%20closer%2C%20fostering%20unity%20and%20integration%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20social%20sector%2C%20an%20initiative%20like%20the%20Sarva%20Shiksha%20Abhiyan%20highlights%20how%20Atal%20Ji%20dreamt%20of%20building%20an%20India%20where%20modern%20education%20is%20accessible%20to%20people%20across%20the%20nation%2C%20particularly%20for%20the%20poor%20and%20marginalised%20sections.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20his%20government%20presided%20over%20many%20economic%20reforms%20which%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20India's%20economic%20surge%20after%20several%20decades%20of%20following%20an%20economic%20philosophy%20which%20encouraged%20cronyism%20and%20stagnation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20then%20went%20on%20to%20underline%20Mr%20Vajpayee's%20leadership%20when%20India%20conducted%20nuclear%20tests%20in%20Pokhran.%20%26quot%3BA%20wonderful%20example%20of%20Vajpayee%20Ji's%20leadership%20can%20be%20seen%20in%20the%20summer%20of%201998.%20His%20Government%20had%20just%20assumed%20office%20and%20on%2011th%20May%2C%20India%20conducted%20the%20Pokhran%20tests%2C%20known%20as%20Operation%20Shakti.%20These%20tests%20exemplified%20the%20prowess%20of%20India's%20scientific%20community.%20The%20world%20was%20stunned%20that%20India%20had%20done%20the%20tests%20and%20expressed%20their%20anger%20in%20no%20uncertain%20terms.%20Any%20ordinary%20leader%20would%20have%20buckled%2C%20but%20Atal%20Ji%20was%20made%20differently.%20And%20what%20happened%3F%20India%20stood%20firm%20and%20resolute%20with%20the%20government%20calling%20for%20another%20set%20of%20tests%20two%20days%20later%2C%20on%2013th%20May!%20If%20the%20tests%20of%20the%2011th%20showed%20scientific%20skill%2C%20the%20ones%20on%2013th%20showed%20true%20leadership.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20message%20to%20the%20world%20that%20gone%20were%20the%20days%20when%20India%20would%20buckle%20under%20threats%20or%20pressure.%20Despite%20facing%20international%20sanctions%2C%20the%20then%20NDA%20government%20of%20Vajpayee%20Ji%20stood%20firm%2C%20articulating%20India's%20right%20to%20safeguard%20its%20sovereignty%20while%20simultaneously%20being%20the%20strongest%20proponent%20of%20world%20peace%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20wrote%20about%20his%20senior%20in%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAtal%20Ji%20understood%20Indian%20democracy%20and%20also%20the%20need%20to%20make%20it%20stronger.%20Atal%20Ji%20presided%20over%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20NDA%2C%20which%20redefined%20coalitions%20in%20Indian%20politics.%20He%20brought%20people%20together%20and%20made%20NDA%20a%20force%20for%20development%2C%20national%20progress%20and%20regional%20ambitions.%20His%20Parliamentary%20brilliance%20was%20seen%20throughout%20his%20political%20journey.%20He%20belonged%20to%20a%20party%20with%20a%20handful%20of%20MPs%20but%20his%20words%20were%20enough%20to%20rattle%20the%20might%20of%20the%20all-powerful%20Congress%20Party%20that%20time.%20As%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20he%20blunted%20the%20criticisms%20of%20the%20Opposition%20with%20style%20and%20substance.%20His%20was%20a%20career%20spent%20largely%20in%20the%20Opposition%20benches%20but%20never%20carried%20any%20trace%20of%20bitterness%20against%20anyone%2C%20even%20though%20the%20Congress%20stooped%20to%20new%20lows%20by%20going%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20calling%20him%20a%20traitor!%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%2C%20he%20wrote%2C%20was%20not%20one%20to%20cling%20on%20to%20power%20through%20opportunistic%20means.%20%26quot%3BHe%20preferred%20to%20resign%20in%201996%20instead%20of%20following%20the%20path%20of%20horse-trading%20and%20dirty%20politics.%20In%201999%2C%20his%20Government%20was%20defeated%20by%201%20vote.%20A%20lot%20of%20people%20told%20him%20to%20challenge%20the%20immoral%20politics%20happening%20then%20but%20he%20preferred%20to%20go%20by%20the%20rules.%20Eventually%2C%20he%20came%20back%20with%20another%20resounding%20mandate%20from%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20elaborated%20how%20Mr%20Vajpayee%20agreed%20to%20merge%20his%20party%20--%20then%20Jan%20Sangh%20--%20with%20the%20Janata%20Party%20to%20challenge%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20government%20after%20the%20Emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20commitment%20to%20protecting%20our%20Constitution%20too%2C%20Atal%20Ji%20stands%20tall.%20He%20was%20deeply%20impacted%20by%20the%20martyrdom%20of%20Dr.%20Syama%20Prasad%20Mookerjee.%20Years%20later%2C%20he%20was%20a%20pillar%20of%20the%20anti-Emergency%20movement.%20In%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%201977%20elections%20after%20the%20Emergency%2C%20he%20agreed%20to%20merger%20of%20his%20own%20Party%20(Jan%20Sangh)%20into%20the%20Janata%20Party.%20I%20am%20sure%20it%20would%20have%20been%20a%20painful%20decision%20for%20him%20and%20the%20others%2C%20but%20safeguarding%20the%20Constitution%20was%20all%20that%20mattered%20to%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20also%20noteworthy%20how%20deeply%20rooted%20Atal%20Ji%20was%20in%20Indian%20culture.%20Upon%20becoming%20India's%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%2C%20he%20became%20the%20first%20Indian%20leader%20to%20speak%20in%20Hindi%20at%20the%20United%20Nations.%20This%20one%20gesture%20showcased%20his%20immense%20pride%20in%20India's%20heritage%20and%20identity%2C%20leaving%20an%20indelible%20mark%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAtal%20Ji's%20persona%20was%20magnetic%20and%20his%20life%20was%20enriched%20by%20his%20love%20for%20literature%20and%20expression.%20A%20prolific%20writer%20and%20poet%2C%20he%20used%20words%20to%20inspire%2C%20provoke%20thought%2C%20and%20even%20offer%20solace.%20His%20poetry%2C%20often%20reflective%20of%20his%20inner%20struggles%20and%20hopes%20for%20the%20nation%2C%20continues%20to%20resonate%20with%20people%20across%20age%20groups%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20said%20it%20was%20a%20privilege%20for%20BJP%20workers%20like%20him%20to%20be%20able%20to%20learn%20from%20the%20stalwart.%20%26quot%3BFor%20so%20many%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20Karyakartas%20like%20me%2C%20it%20is%20our%20privilege%20that%20we%20were%20able%20to%20learn%20and%20interact%20with%20a%20person%20like%20Atal%20Ji.%20His%20contribution%20to%20the%20BJP%20was%20foundational.%20In%20those%20days%20to%20spearhead%20an%20alternative%20narrative%20to%20the%20dominant%20Congress%20showed%20his%20greatness.%20Alongside%20stalwarts%20like%20Shri%20LK%20Advani%20Ji%20and%20Dr%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi%20Ji%20he%20nurtured%20the%20party%20from%20its%20formative%20years%2C%20guiding%20it%20through%20challenges%2C%20setbacks%20and%20triumphs.%20Whenever%20the%20choice%20came%20between%20ideology%20and%20power%2C%20he%20always%20chose%20the%20former.%20He%20was%20able%20to%20convince%20the%20nation%20that%20an%20alternative%20world%20view%20from%20the%20Congress%20was%20possible%20and%20such%20a%20worldview%20could%20deliver.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20his%20100th%20Jayanti%2C%20let%20us%20rededicate%20ourselves%20to%20realising%20his%20ideals%20and%20fulfilling%20his%20vision%20for%20India.%20Let%20us%20strive%20to%20build%20an%20India%20that%20embodies%20his%20principles%20of%20good%20governance%2C%20unity%2C%20and%20progress.%20Atal%20Ji's%20unwavering%20belief%20in%20the%20potential%20of%20our%20nation%20continues%20to%20inspire%20us%20to%20aim%20higher%20and%20work%20harder%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735098420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F1jkst9mo_modi-atal_625x300_25_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstands-tall-as-a-statesman-pm-narendra-modi-remembers-atal-bihari-vajpayee-7326674%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20stands%20tall%20as%20a%20statesman%20and%20continues%20to%20inspire%20countless%20people%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20wrote%20today%2C%20paying%20tribute%20to%20the%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20on%20his%20birth%20centenary.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstands-tall-as-a-statesman-pm-narendra-modi-remembers-atal-bihari-vajpayee-7326674%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NYC%20subway%20horror%3A%20Why%20no%20one%20stopped%20illegal%20immigrant%20accused%3F%20Woman%20burned%20alive%20while%20bystanders%2C%20NYPD%20cop%20'Ignored'%20victim%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735098212000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116646787%2Cimgsize-1169157.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fnyc-subway-horror-why-no-one-stopped-illegal-immigrant-accused-