ths.%20Former%20England%20captains%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Michael%20Atherton%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F110-michael-atherton-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMichael%20Atherton%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Nasser%20Hussain%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F234-nasser-hussain-playerprofile%5C%22%3ENasser%20Hussain%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20a%20detailed%20virtual%20conversation%20with%20Ashwin%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20in%20Chennai%20following%20his%20retirement%20from%20international%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20interaction%2C%20Ashwin%20gave%20some%20interesting%20insights%20into%20his%20memoir%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BI%20Have%20The%20Streets%3A%20A%20Kutty%20Cricket%20Story%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20which%20was%20released%20earlier%20this%20year%20in%20July.%20During%20the%20chat%2C%20Ashwin%20opened%20up%20on%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20myths%20about%20him.%20He%20said%20that%20people%20think%20that%20he%20is%20too%20serious%20and%20doesn't%20enjoy%20the%20game%20as%20much%20as%20someone%20like%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Ashwin's%20insisted%20that's%20not%20the%20case%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20gets%20lost%20while%20playing%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20people%20to%20know%20me%20for%20who%20I%20am%2C%20because%20a%20lot%20of%20times%2C%20Ashwin's%20picking%20up%20a%20wicket%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20is%20all%20over%20the%20place.%20He's%20just%20jumping%20about%20and%20people%20very%20often%20tend%20to%20believe%20that%20Ashwin's%20the%20one%20that's%20absolutely%20serious%20and%20Virat's%20the%20one%20that's%20having%20all%20the%20fun%2C%20which%20is%20why%20somebody%20asked%20me%20the%20question%2C%20why%20are%20you%20serious%20all%20the%20time%3F%20My%20answer%20to%20that%20in%20the%20first%20place%20is%20I'm%20never%20a%20serious%20person%2C%20but%20when%20somebody%20is%20clobbering%20me%20and%20I%20have%20the%20ball%20in%20my%20hand%20to%20win%20a%20Test%20Match%20for%20my%20country%2C%20my%20mind%20is%20sticking%2C%20because%20I'm%20in%20the%20process.%20So%20very%20often%2C%20you%20don't%20see%20me%20picking%20up%20a%20five-wicket%20haul%20and%20pushing%20across%20a%20kiss%20through%20the%20blade%20of%20my%20bat%20to%20my%20better%20half%20sitting%20in%20the%20dressing%20room%20or%20sitting%20in%20the%20hospitality%20box.%20So%20I%20felt%20like%20a%20lot%20of%20who%20I%20am%20got%20diluted%20in%20the%20fact%20of%20what%20I've%20become.%20So%20I%20wanted%20to%20bring%20that%20out%20in%20my%20book%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20said%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJhdrN_5F4DY%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESky%20Sports%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20cricket%20has%20been%20blessed%20to%20witness%20greats%20of%20the%20game%20like%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sachin%20Tendulkar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F14-sachin-tendulkar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESachin%20Tendulkar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20often%20get%20worshipped%20like%20gods.However%2C%20Ashwin%20feels%20it's%20harsh%20to%20sideline%20others%20as%20cricket%20is%20a%20team%20sport.%20But%2C%20for%20Ashwin%2C%20he%20has%20always%20been%20the%20Most%20Valuable%20Player%20(MVP)%20of%20his%20own%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20talk%20about%2C%20when%20they%20talk%20about%20Indian%20cricket%2C%20that's%20one%20thing%20I%20want%20to%20change%20over%20the%20years.%20They%20talk%20about%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20they%20have%20been%20talking%20about%20Rohit%20over%20the%20years.%20When%20I%20grew%20up%2C%20I%20spoke%20a%20lot%20about%20Sachin%2C%20I%20spoke%20about%20other%20superstars%2C%20the%20celebrities.%20One%20message%20I%20would%20leave%20for%20everybody%20and%20I%20want%20to%20constantly%20change%20is%20that%20it's%20not%20the%20fact%20that%20these%20are%20glorious%20cricketers%20but%20people%20on%20the%20outside%20who%20believe%20that%20everyone%20plays%20a%20support%20cast%20are%20extremely%20wrong%20because%20this%20is%20a%20sport.%20An%20MVP%20in%20my%20life%2C%20for%20my%20dad%20or%20for%20my%20mom%2C%20I%20am%20the%20MVP.%20It's%20not%20Rohit%2C%20Virat%20or%20somebody%20on%20the%20outside%2C%20likewise%2C%20everyone's%20journey%20is%20unique.%20For%20me%2C%20I%20have%20always%20been%20the%20MVP%20and%20I%20am%20the%20MVP%20of%20my%20cricket%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735097760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fhgesnsng_r-ashwin-afp_625x300_20_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fi-am-mvp-of-my-cricket-not-rohit-sharma-or-virat-kohli-ravichandran-ashwin-7320637%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20doesn't%20want%20people%20to%20celebrate%20his%20career%20or%20worship%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fi-am-mvp-of-my-cricket-not-rohit-sharma-or-virat-kohli-ravichandran-ashwin-7320637%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inside%20pics%20from%20Alia-Ranbir's%20Christmas%20eve%20dinner%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1735097651000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116646683%2Cimgsize-51620.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsoni-razdan-shares-inside-pics-from-alia-bhatt-ranbir-kapoor-and-rahas-christmas-eve-dinner%2Fartic