%20into%20her%20trailer%20unannounced%20while%20she%20was%20undressed%20and%20breastfeeding%2C%20among%20other%20offenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBryan%20Freedman%2C%20an%20attorney%20representing%20Baldini%2C%20Abel%2C%20Nathan%2C%20and%20their%20companies%2C%20previously%20called%20Lively's%20allegations%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20false%2C%20outrageous%20and%20intentionally%20salacious.%26quot%3B%20Freedman%20didn't%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELively's%20complaint%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblake-lively-lawsuit-justin-baldoni-lawsuit-pr-law-experts-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewielding%20numerous%20text%20messages%20and%20emails%20her%20lawyers%20obtained%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20also%20alleged%20Baldoni%20worked%20with%20Abel%20and%20Nathan%20on%20a%20sophisticated%20public%20relations%20campaign%20through%20manipulated%20social%20media%20activity%20and%20stories%20published%20in%20tabloids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20know%20we%20can%20bury%20anyone%2C%26quot%3B%20Nathan%20wrote%20to%20Abel%20in%20a%20February%20text%20message%20included%20in%20Lively's%20complaint%20as%20they%20discussed%20how%20to%20propose%20the%20communications%20strategy%20to%20Baldoni.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELively's%20complaint%20alleges%20the%20campaign%20on%20behalf%20of%20Baldoni%20unfolded%20in%20secret%20alongside%20the%20public%20relations%20campaign%20for%20the%20movie%2C%20which%20was%20released%20in%20theaters%20in%20August%20and%20grossed%20over%20%24350%20million%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJones%20said%20in%20her%20lawsuit%20she%20fired%20Abel%20in%20August%20after%20she%20had%20%26quot%3Bstolen%20more%20than%2070%20proprietary%20and%20sensitive%20business%20documents%26quot%3B%20as%20well%20as%20client%20information.%20Abel%20also%20tried%20to%20poach%20employees%20for%20a%20competing%20public%20relations%20firm%2C%20RWA%20Communications%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20alle