s%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20time%20snowboarding%20was%20with%20a%20friend%20who%20grew%20up%20skiing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20each%20stepped%20into%20the%20massive%20snowboard%20boots%2C%20she%20exclaimed%20how%20comfortable%20they%20were.%20To%20me%2C%20they%20felt%20awkward%20and%20bulky%2C%20but%20she%20promised%20that%20they%20were%20far%20more%20comfortable%20than%20any%20pair%20of%20ski%20boots%20she%20ever%20wore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20year%20later%2C%20I%20finally%20understood%20what%20she%20meant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ski%20boots%20I%20wore%20were%20coated%20in%20a%20hard%20plastic%20shell%2C%20which%20meant%20my%20feet%20didn't%20have%20much%20flexibility%20inside%20the%20shoe.%20They%20also%20had%20two%20awkward%20bumps%20at%20the%20front%20and%20back%20of%20each%20boot%20for%20ski%20clips%2C%20making%20it%20feel%20like%20I%20was%20never%20walking%20on%20a%20flat%20surface.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimple%20tasks%20like%20walking%20downstairs%20were%20challenging.%20Meanwhile%2C%20my%20snowboard%20boots%20had%20a%20softer%20and%20cushier%20interior%20and%20the%20bottoms%20were%20completely%20flat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20mind%20wearing%20the%20snowboard%20boots%20all%20day%2C%20but%20I%20couldn't%20wait%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20ski%20boots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOn%20skis%2C%20you%20face%20down%20the%20mountain.%20On%20a%20snowboard%2C%20you're%20perpendicular.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side-by-side%20images%20of%20the%20author%20skiing%20and%20snowboarding.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63e5681d96242f0019e83964%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESide-by-side%20images%20of%20the%20reporter%20skiing%20and%20snowboarding.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20differences%20between%20the%20two%20spo