%20while%20snowboarding%20and%20skiing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20trying%20the%20two%2C%20I%20learned%20skiers%20have%20it%20way%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20most%20skiers%2C%20myself%20included%2C%20use%20poles.%20With%20my%20poles%2C%20I%20could%20push%20myself%20on%20flat%20patches%20and%20propel%20myself%20forward.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESnowboarders%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20don't%20have%20poles.%20I%20needed%20to%20prioritize%20momentum%20during%20any%20flat%20area%2C%20and%20if%20I%20ended%20up%20coming%20to%20a%20stop%2C%20I%20needed%20to%20unclip%20my%20back%20foot%20and%20skate%20around.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESkating%20on%20a%20snowboard%20was%20utterly%20exhausting%2C%20and%20after%20trying%20skiing%2C%20I%20longed%20for%20the%20ease%20of%20poles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20fell%20a%20lot%20more%20learning%20to%20snowboard.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20in%20a%20patch%20of%20trees%20after%20falling%20on%20her%20snowboard.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63e55c6627e5db0018eefb2f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20reporter%20in%20a%20patch%20of%20trees%20after%20falling%20on%20her%20snowboard.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20my%20first%20snowboarding%20lesson%2C%20I%20crowdsourced%20advice%20and%20tips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20single%20person%20told%20me%20to%20prepare%20to%20fall.%20A%20lot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20into%20the%20class%20expecting%20my%20fair%20share%20of%20topples%2C%20but%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20just%20how%20often%20I%20would%20find%20myself%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20four-hour%20snowboarding%20class%2C%20I%20fell%20dozens%20of%20times.%20When%20I%20hit%20the%20slopes%2C%20I%20was%20on%20the%20ground%20more%20than%20I%20was%20standing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20went%20into%20my%20skiing%20lesson%2C%20I%20expected%20the%20same%20number%20of%20falls.%20During%20the%20four-house%20lesson%2C%20I%20didn't%20fall%20a%20single%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20did%20attempt%20a%20green%20run%20later%20that%20day%20and%20fell%20a%20few%20times%2C%20but%20it%20still%20didn't%20come%20close%20to%20the%20number%20of%20falls%20I%20took%20during%20my%20first%20day%20of%20snowboarding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGetting%20on%20and%20off%20lifts%20was%20easier%20on%20skis.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20family%20of%20skiers%20gets%20off%20a%20lift.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63e55ec327e5db0018eefbfa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20family%20of%20skiers%20gets%20off%20a%20lift.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20place%20where%20I%20struggled%20as%20a%20beginner%20snowboarder%20was%20getting%20on%20and%20off%20the%20ski%20lifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20lift%20ends%2C%20it%20doesn't%20stop%20moving.%20Instead%2C%20skiers%20and%20snowboarders%20must%20hop%20off%20their%20seats%20and%20ski%20or%20snowboard%20down%20a%20slight%20decline%20to%20the%20start%20of%20their%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20ski%20poles%20were%20a%20major%20advantage%20in%20this%20situation.%20When%20I%20got%20off%20a%20lift%20on%20skis%2C%20I%20felt%20sturdy%20and%20confident.%20I%20never%20fell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20off%20a%20lift%20on%20a%20snowboard%2C%20however%2C%20seemed%20like%20a%20skill%20within%20itself.%20I%20had%20to%20keep%20my%20balance%20while%20pushing%20off%20the%20lift.%20The%20result%20was%20fall%20after%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20my%20first%20day%20of%20snowboarding%2C%20I%20didn't%20successfully%20get%20off%20one%20single%20lift%20without%20falling.%20Meanwhile%2C%20I%20navigated%20lifts%20easily%20on%20my%20first%20day%20of%20skiing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv