igcaption%3EThe%20author%20snowboarding%20at%20the%20Winter%20Park%20Resort.%3Cp%3EKatie%20Sproles%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20two%20winters%20in%20Colorado%2C%20I%20imagine%20I've%20heard%20the%20phrase%20close%20to%20a%20hundred%20times%20from%20friends.%20And%20I've%20recited%20it%20nearly%20as%20much%20to%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20after%20trying%20both%2C%20I'm%20starting%20to%20understand%20why%20it's%20said%20so%20often.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20my%20first%20day%20on%20a%20snowboard%20last%20year%20was%20disastrous%2C%20my%20second%20day%20went%20much%20smoother.%20By%20the%20end%20of%20day%20two%2C%20I%20could%20get%20down%20blue%20runs%2C%20and%20after%20about%20five%20days%2C%20I%20felt%20confident%20navigating%20on%20the%20heelside%20and%20toeside%20edges%20of%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20quite%20as%20confident%20yet%20with%20skiing.%20I've%20skied%20only%20one%20day%2C%20and%20although%20I%20fell%20far%20less%20than%20I%20did%20snowboarding%2C%20keeping%20my%20feet%20perfectly%20parallel%20seems%20like%20a%20skill%20that%20would%20take%20months%2C%20if%20not%20years%2C%20to%20master.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20trying%20both%2C%20I%20think%20there's%20nothing%20like%20gliding%20down%20a%20snowy%20mountain%20on%20a%20sunny%20day%20%E2%80%94%20regardless%20of%20whether%20you're%20on%20skis%20or%20a%20snowboard.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20holds%20a%20snowboard.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63e6599d96242f0019e84e5a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20holds%20a%20snowboard.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20sports%20have%20their%20pros%20and%20cons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20I've%20spent%20more%20time%20on%20a%20snowboard%20overall%2C%20I'm%20sticking%20with%20that%20for%20now.%20I