opener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F363502%2Firis-strill-bishwadeep-moitra-silaiwali-upcycled-ragdolls-empower-afghan-women-refugees-financial-freedom%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efamilies%E2%80%99%20livelihoods%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20yet%20their%20efforts%20often%20go%20unnoticed.%20By%20placing%20women%E2%80%99s%20names%20on%20doorplates%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20give%20them%20the%20recognition%20and%20dignity%20they%20deserve.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20support%20of%20Paramjit%20Singh%20Bhullar%20and%20a%20few%20other%20women%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EPanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Sheshandeep%20executed%20her%20plan.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20confident%20that%20I%20had%20the%20support%20of%20my%20team%2C%20and%20with%20the%20available%20funds%2C%20we%20could%20bring%20my%20plan%20to%20life.%20The%20idea%20of%20adding%20nameplates%20for%20women%20was%20within%20our%20budget.%20So%2C%20we%20swiftly%20moved%20forward%2C%20using%20the%20resources%20already%20allocated%20to%20the%20village.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20around%20110%20households%20in%20the%20village%2C%20Sheshandeep%E2%80%99s%20initiative%20saw%20the%20nameplates%20of%20women%20proudly%20displayed%20on%20every%20door%20in%20the%20village.%20The%20results%20were%20immediate%20and%20impactful.%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20one%20young%20woman%20who%20came%20to%20me%2C%20with%20tears%20in%20her%20eyes%2C%20thanking%20me%20for%20this%20initiative.%20She%20said%20she%20had%20never%20been%20allowed%20to%20leave%20her%20home%20or%20make%20decisions%20for%20herself.%20But%20now%2C%20when%20she%20saw%20her%20name%20on%20the%20doorplate%2C%20she%20felt%20proud%20and%20recognised%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sheshandeep%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ripples%20of%20change%20were%20felt%20across%20the%20village.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20family%2C%20no%20one%20objected%20to%20the%20nameplate.%20I%20am%20proud%20that%20my%20name%20is%20recognised%20alongside%20the%20men%E2%80%99s.%20It%20shows%20that%20we%20are%20equal%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rani%20Kaur%2C%20a%2042-year-old%20woman%20from%20Manak%20Khana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20see%20my%20name%20on%20the%20doorplate%2C%20I%20feel%20proud.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20a%20name%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20recognition%20of%20who%20I%20am.%20It%20gives%20me%20a%20sense%20of%20identity%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jaspreet%20Kaur%2C%20a%20younger%20resident%20of%20the%20village.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20incredible%20to%20see%20the%20change%20in%20the%20mindset%20of%20the%20younger%20generation.%20They%20see%20women%20leading%2C%20and%20they%20aspire%20to%20be%20like%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Paramjit%20Singh%20Bhullar%2C%20who%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20bringing%20to%20life%20the%20initiative%2C%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20small%20step%2C%20but%20it%20made%20a%20huge%20difference.%20For%20generations%2C%20our%20society%20had%20only%20recognised%20men.%20Sheshandeep%E2%80%99s%20vision%20was%20fresh%2C%20and%20it%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F291700%2Fruma-devi-barmer-invited-by-harvard-for-empowering-women-via-fashion%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egave%20women%20the%20recognition%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20had%20always%20deserved.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20new%20phase%2C%20a%20shared%20vision%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20her%20term%20as%20%3Cem%3ESarpanch%3C%2Fem%3E%20ended%20in%20March%202024%2C%20Sheshandeep%20continued%20to%20work%20towards%20the%20betterment%20of%20women%20in%20her%20village.%20She%20is%20now%20leading%20a%20project%20with%20%E2%80%98Read%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20an%20initiative%20that%20teaches%20skills%20like%20stitching%20and%20computer%20literacy%20to%20marginalised%20women%20in%20the%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3